<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>烘焙奶爸 Papa Bakes</title>
  <meta name="description" content="用父親的愛，做出孩子愛吃的。結構化烘焙教學 app。">
  <style>
    :root { --accent: #e2853c; --text: #1a1a1a; --muted: #666; --bg: #faf8f6; }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang TC", "Hiragino Sans", sans-serif;
           margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.6; }
    header { padding: 3rem 1.5rem 2rem; text-align: center; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
    .tagline { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .lang { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
    .lang a { color: var(--accent); margin: 0 .75rem; }
    main { max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.06); }
    h2 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-top: 0; }
    footer { text-align: center; padding: 2rem 1rem; color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; }
    footer a { color: var(--accent); }
    .badge { display: inline-block; background: #fff3e8; color: var(--accent);
             padding: .2rem .6rem; border-radius: 999px; font-size: .85rem; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <p class="badge">iOS App</p>
    <h1>烘焙奶爸 <span style="font-weight:400;color:var(--muted)">Papa Bakes</span></h1>
    <p class="tagline">用父親的愛，做出孩子愛吃的。<br>Made with a dad's love.</p>
    <p class="lang">
      <a href="privacy.html">隱私權政策 Privacy</a>
      <a href="mailto:howly7777777@gmail.com">聯絡我們 Contact</a>
    </p>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>關於 About</h2>
      <p>烘焙奶爸是為家庭烘焙設計的結構化教學 app：圖文步驟、內建計時器、份量換算，以及「為什麼這樣做」的原理說明與失敗排查。基礎與中級免費，高級食譜與奶爸心得可訂閱 Papa Bakes Plus 解鎖。</p>
      <p>Papa Bakes is a structured home-baking app for parents: step-by-step photos, built-in timers, serving scaling, science notes and troubleshooting. Basic &amp; intermediate recipes are free; advanced recipes and Papa's notes unlock with Papa Bakes Plus.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <h2>支援 Support</h2>
      <p>問題、建議或訂閱相關事宜，請來信：<br>
      <a href="mailto:howly7777777@gmail.com">howly7777777@gmail.com</a></p>
      <p>For questions, feedback or subscription help:<br>
      <a href="mailto:howly7777777@gmail.com">howly7777777@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Papa Bakes 烘焙奶爸 &middot; <a href="privacy.html">Privacy 隱私權</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
